<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 of 28 October 1996 on the common organization of the markets in processed fruit and vegetable products (1), and in particular Article 10 (4) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse puu- ja k&ouml;&ouml;giviljatooteturu &uuml;hist korraldust k&auml;sitlevat n&otilde;ukogu 28. oktoobri 1996. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 2201/96, (1) eriti selle artikli 10 l&otilde;iget 4, ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 10 of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 provides for specific measures to promote products of importance at local or regional level which face strong international competition; whereas white asparagus for processing meets these criteria; whereas, in addition, in the case of asparagus for processing, Article 10 (3) provides for the grant of a flat-rate aid per hectare to facilitate the introduction of specific measures; whereas detailed rules must therefore be laid down for the application of those provisions; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2201/96 artiklis 10 n&auml;hakse ette erimeetmed selliste kohalikul v&otilde;i piirkondlikul tasandil suure t&auml;htsusega toodete m&uuml;&uuml;gi edendamiseks, mis on tugevasse rahvusvahelisse konkurentsi sattunud; t&ouml;&ouml;tlemiseks m&otilde;eldud pleegitatud spargel vastab k&otilde;nealustele kriteeriumidele; peale selle n&auml;hakse artikli 10 l&otilde;ikes 3 ette t&ouml;&ouml;tlemiseks m&otilde;eldud pleegitatud spargli puhul kindlasummaline hektaritoetus, et h&otilde;lbustada erimeetmete rakendamist; seet&otilde;ttu tuleb kehtestada k&otilde;nealuste s&auml;tete &uuml;ksikasjalikud rakenduseeskirjad; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in the interests of efficiency, measures should be implemented to improve the competitiveness of the sector by means of programmes to be proposed and implemented by representative associations consisting of producers' organizations and associations of processors, and the conditions for their representativeness should be defined with reference both to the production region and to Community production; </inglise>
<eesti> t&otilde;hususe huvides tuleks rakendada meetmeid sektori konkurentsiv&otilde;ime parandamiseks programmide abil, mille pakkujateks ja rakendajateks on esindavad &uuml;hingud, mis koosnevad tootjaorganisatsioonidest ja t&ouml;&ouml;tlejate &uuml;hendustest ning mille representatiivsuse tingimused tuleks m&auml;&auml;ratleda nii tootmispiirkonda kui ka &uuml;henduse tootmist arvesse v&otilde;ttes; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in view of the requirements of the sector, two different rates of Community financing should be fixed, according to the type of measure to be financed, as well as two ceilings on Community financing, depending on how representative the associations are; whereas, in order to facilitate the calculation of the ceiling by the representative associations, it should be laid down that the ceiling is calculated with reference to the value of production of representative associations during the three-year period 1994 to 1996; </inglise>
<eesti> sektori n&otilde;udeid silmas pidades tuleks vastavalt finantseeritava meetme liigile kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata &uuml;hendusepoolse finantseerimise kaks erinevat protsendim&auml;&auml;ra ning kaks &uuml;hendusepoolse finantseerimise &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;ra olenevalt &uuml;hingute representatiivsusest; h&otilde;lbustamaks esindavatele &uuml;hingutele &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;ra arvutamist tuleks ette n&auml;ha, et &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;ra arvutamisel v&otilde;etakse arvesse esindavate &uuml;hingute toodangu v&auml;&auml;rtust kolme aasta jooksul, aastail 1994-1996; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in the interests of sound management, the information and undertakings to be included in the programmes of specific measures, the measures to be excluded, the time-limit for approval by the Member States and the procedure for any amendment of the programmes should be defined; </inglise>
<eesti> usaldusv&auml;&auml;rse juhtimise huvides tuleks m&auml;&auml;ratleda info ja kohustused, mida erimeetmete programm peab sisaldama, meetmed, mis tuleb v&auml;lja j&auml;tta, programmi liikmesriikide poolt kinnitamise t&auml;htaeg ning v&otilde;imalike muudatuste tegemise kord; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas provision should be made for a single advance payment subject to the appropriate securities and for six-monthly payments restricted to 85 % of the amount of the financial contribution; whereas it should be specified that the security will be released when the balance of the financial contribution is paid; whereas the activities of the associations should be monitored by means of periodical reports; </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks ette n&auml;ha asjaomaste tagatiste esitamisega seotud &uuml;hekordne ettemakse ning kuue kuu maksed, mis piirduvad 85% rahalisest toetusest; tuleks t&auml;psustada, et rahalise toetuse l&otilde;ppmakse tegemisel tagatis vabastatakse; &uuml;hingute tegevust tuleks j&auml;lgida perioodiliste aruannete abil; </eesti>
